text: Skull and Crown is a 1935 American western movie directed by Elmer Clifton and starring Rin Tin Tin, Jr., Regis Toomey, Jack Mulhall, Jack Mower, Molly O'Day, Lois January, Tom London. It was distributed by Reliable Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1935 movies Category:1930s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Elmer Clifton
